(*****************)(***************/*) Voted and received a NO messages, it aborts                  [](\E i \in Proc : (fd["YES"] /\ self # PC_IDS[self]) =>     ****         ***          **           Tran Thanh Hai        igor@dcc.uchile             *)      ()
